  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2.\u0d91\u0db8\u0dca.\u0d91\u0dc6\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dba\u0ddd \u0dc3\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "IMF representatives meet Sajith",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A meeting between a delegation of the International Monetary Fund and Mr. Sajith Premadasa, the leader of the opposition, was held in Colombo today (30).",
        "The meeting was held at the office of the opposition leader in Marx Fernando Mawatha, Colombo, as part of a round of discussions aimed at providing solutions to the financial crisis that Sri Lanka is facing.",
        "The opposition leader's office states that the country's economic situation was discussed at length.",
        "Samagi Jana Balawegaya MPs Dr. Harsha de Silva, Iran Wickramaratne, Kabir Hashim, Rauf Hakeem, Niroshan Perera and others attended the meeting."
      ],
